The Automotive Cloud clinical data model is similar to the FHIR® standard. This supports easier and more straightforward clinical data integration from other source systems. When devising an implementation strategy, you or your integration partner map messages from the EHR system to the correct Automotive Cloud object. Data is replicated into the clinical data model with read-only access. Data that originates in the EHR or other clinical systems is view-only, so the source system remains the system of record.

    1. Person Accounts must be enabled in your org
    2. Conversion requires a 1:1 Account to Contact relationship, so create additional accounts as needed to allow each Contact you are converting to have their own account.
    3. The Account and Contact must have the same record owner.
    4. The Parent Account field on the Account must be blank.
    5. The Reports To field on the Contact must be blank.
    6. The Account is not set as a Parent account for any other accounts.
